Introduction

(M)IRROR, also stylized just as MIRROR, and known pre-debut as VT Trainee, was a 5-member boy group under VT Entertainment. The members were Sunho, Zeo, Sol, Dojun, and Youngwon.

They made their debut on May 12, 2023, with the single album "백월(白月)". Sadly the group disbanded only a few months later.
